Title: When Push Comes to Shove (1)
Plot: After somehow seeing Capt. Kenneth Push in a vision at a murder scene, Allison calls upon his assistance to find a serial killer. However, the only way Capt. Push can help is by literally putting his life on the line.
GuestStars: Joel Kramer,  Zoe Simpson, Kelly McNair, Randy Mulkey, Christopher Hoffman, Saida Pagan, Lyn Alicia Henderson, Reggie Jordan, John O'Brien, Neal Matarazzo, Phil Reeves, Arliss Howard
